{
  "texts": [
    "However, it is crucial to acknowledge the limitations of LLMs, particularly their potential to perpetuate biases present in their training data.",
    "Therefore, it is essential for educators to apply human oversight to complement and verify LLM-based assessment.",
    "LLMs in educational assessments can also generate valuable analytics and insights into student performance.",
    "These insights20 can help educators understand learning patterns, identify common misconceptions, and make data-driven instructional decisions 21.",
    "Automatic scoring systems have become more precise, adaptive, and context-aware with the introduction of LLMs, such as Chat GPT, which provide an extensive knowledge base and contextual understanding of the table, supplemented by domainspecific expertise 9."
  ]
}